# Allowlist: exclude everything, then include only what the build needs.
# Workaround for Fly remote builder sometimes ignoring normal exclusions (1.2GB+ context).
# Breed avatars are served from Fly volume at /data/breed-avatars; do not send them.

**
!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!nginx.conf
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!index.html
!vite.config.ts
!tsconfig.json
!src
!public
# Re-exclude large dir (kept in repo; served from volume at runtime)
public/assets/breed-avatars
